{"tid":884973,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(左膠做戲屈中共?) 民主黨辦事處外遭縱火, 李卓人文宣被焚毀","createTime":"2018-11-01T04:22:21.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-01T06:37:06.000Z","uid":134071,"like":3,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"7532df52769d5412c67cb9dd640574f8dd159530","tid":884973,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T04:22:21.000Z","msg":"應該係左膠自已放火燒自己, 屈中共屈本土派?  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n01:<br />\n<br />\n【九西補選】民主黨幸福邨辦事處外遭縱火　一箱李卓人文宣被焚毀<br />\n<br />\n撰文：吳倬安<br />\n2018-11-01 12:04<br />\n最後更新日期：2018-11-01 12:04<br />\n<br />\n民協社區主任徐溢軒今天早上在Facebook表示，一盒擺放在民主黨幸福邨地區辦事處的李卓人宣傳單遭焚毀，他已就事件報警，並強烈譴責縱火行為，又重申不容暴力干預選舉。<br />\n<br />\n民協社區主任徐溢軒今天早上在Facebook表示，一箱擺放在民主黨幸福邨地區辦事處的李卓人宣傳單遭焚毀，他已就事件報警。<br />\n<br />\n徐溢軒表示，今早他為李卓人擺放宣傳街站後，返回民主黨深水埗區議員鄒穎恒位於幸福邨的地區辦事處，發現擺放在門外、其中一箱呼籲「1125」補選投票日支持李卓人的宣傳單張遭焚毀。他已就事件報警。<br />\n<br />\n徐溢軒指，幸福邨過去治安良好，未有發生類似事件。他說即使意見不同，也不能以此手法限制表達政治立場，強烈譴責縱火行為，並重申不容暴力干預選舉。"},{"pid":"95a57817c6b22d53a758c678e9ea1c15c3eacaba","tid":884973,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T04:23:52.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.facebook.com/TsuiRonald/photos/a.172507306658303/348194635756235/?type=3&amp;theater\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FTsuiRonald%2Fphotos%2Fa.172507306658303%2F348194635756235%2F%3Ftype%3D3%26theater&d=uXNkVBNXjWnhZA1iHhmX7bIOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=99ee8814\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.facebook.com/TsuiRonald/photos/a.172507306658303/348194635756235/?type=3&amp;theater</a><br />\n<br />\n徐溢軒 Ronald Tsui<br />\n讚好此專頁 &middot; 1 小時 &middot; <br />\n <br />\n【強烈遺譴責縱火行為，不容暴力干預選舉】<br />\n<br />\n今早阿軒開完街站後返辦事處，在門外發現其中一箱呼籲1125補選投票日支持李卓人的宣傳單張遭焚毀！雖然火勢未有蔓延，但阿軒認為事態嚴重，已報警處理。<br />\n<br />\n幸福邨過去治安良好，未有發生類似事件，阿軒堅信即使意見不同，也不能以此手法限制表達政治立場。阿軒強烈譴責縱火行為，並重申不容暴力干預選舉！<br />\n<br />\n#強烈譴責縱火行為 #不容暴力干預選舉<br />\n#守護幸福 #支持3號李卓人<br />\n<br />\n民協 ADPL"},{"pid":"10b6b6aa4494c9737b90185fff531de539dc21b2","tid":884973,"uid":53062,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T04:25:03.000Z","msg":"你冇證據屈同土共有咩分別"},{"pid":"54d07f27d8cb57a8afed293103912c757b0b1c85","tid":884973,"uid":134071,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"10b6b6aa4494c9737b90185fff531de539dc21b2","tid":884973,"uid":53062,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T04:25:03.000Z","msg":"你冇證據屈同土共有咩分別"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T04:27:20.000Z","msg":"飯民左膠成日屈人， 仲衰過土共<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c5666e11198b1c8f9ca50eea07e8e200d203540","tid":884973,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T04:31:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64ae080a87db71fd7f0c0c261e9c248f704396ea","tid":884973,"uid":70040,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T04:31:05.000Z","msg":"同美國民主黨一鳩樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eebef397d9a227dab1358d496a6440d4c721bcdd","tid":884973,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"64ae080a87db71fd7f0c0c261e9c248f704396ea","tid":884973,"uid":70040,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T04:31:05.000Z","msg":"同美國民主黨一鳩樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T04:37:52.000Z","msg":"左膠係中共跟本土派既共同敵人（所以中共都阻止希婆當選）"},{"pid":"32f8fe9b2607756bef2b2a2cb006b37e87bfcbef","tid":884973,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T04:44:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09f522ba0fc5a1f87108448